NAME

MojoX::CPAN::Uploader - Mojo way to upload on CPAN

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SYNOPSIS

        mojo-cpanup --user=user --pass=pass file.tar.gz
        mojo-cpanup --user=user file.tar.gz
        mojo-cpanup file.tar.gz
        mojo-cpanup file.tar.gz subdir


DEPENDENCIES

Mojolicious.


